modName: Xenius High Quality Eyes - Elven Recolor
summary: Recolors some of the elven eyes from Xenius eye replacer mod
descriptionHtml:
This mod simply recolors some of the elven eyes from [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/726673]Xenius's[/url] [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/498]High Quality Eyes mod[/url] to match my taste.
The following files were replaced, and between parentheses is the color that they were replaced by:

Bosmer:
1- woodelfdeepbrown (dark brown)Â 
2- woodelfdeepviolet (reddish violet)
3- woodelflightbrown (light brown)

Dunmer:
1- darkelfdeepred (red)
2- darkelfdeepred2 (lightblue)

Altmer:
1- highelfdarkyellow (yellow)
2- highelforange (light green)
3- highelfyellow (orange)

All credits go to [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/726673]Xenius[/url] for the original textures (i used the desaturated version for this), and his [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/498]original mod[/url] is highly recommended to use alongside this for a complete look (just let these files override theirs)
author: Mateo
